Idea Text: R6.4 - Management and governance of resources, infrastructures and ecosystems related to water through the use of decision support systems, blockchain as well as virtual reality and augmented reality
R6.1 - IoT technologies for monitoring all kinds of water facilities, networks and ecosystems

R6.3 - Intelligent techniques for the prediction and detection of failures and breaks in water infrastructures, as well as the detection of variables or parameters for which there is no specific sensorization
R6.5 - Use of machine learning techniques to improve the prediction models of existing water systems
R6.2 - Digital Twins on water infrastructures, on water-linked ecosystems and contaminatino process that allow their study, experimentation and dissemination
